title: Ep. 163 S&A Investor - Insight from the Best Picker on the Internet
itunes:title: Insight from the Best Picker on the Internet
description:
Since 1997, MSN Money columnist Jim Jubak has built one of the most stellar track records on the web. His Jubak Picks portfolio has gained an average annual return of 20.9%. 
On this week's podcast, Jubak talks about his investment strategies and shares some of his favorite companies.
